      'georgy.guide.baby': '<h4>Baby in cups</h4><ul><li><strong>Arugula</strong> — up to 6 cuts per plant (up to 8 at T≥30°C), 10–18 g/cup.</li><li><strong>Baby lettuce</strong> — up to 12 cuts below 30°C, 6–8 at T≥30°C; 20–30 g/cut; −15–20% mass when hot.</li><li>Cut interval <strong>8–18 d</strong> by leaf size.</li><li><strong>2 rows</strong> in channel, <strong>10–19 channels</strong> wide (≤2 m), 80–110 cups/m².</li><li>Area yield — with <strong>timely replanting</strong>; unlimited cuts per place.</li></ul>',
